Let‚Äôs talk about $NEIRO 

And what the hell is going on right now.

First let‚Äôs look at market caps of the top 4 biggest $NEIRO tokens on the biggest blockchains - $ETH and $SOL

The first 2 $NEIRO tokens that I found were both launched on #SOLANA and the following week the second 2 $NEIRO coins I found were on #ETH 

These are the current mcaps of all 4

1. $NEIRO pump fun: $10 million mcap 
2. $NEIRO Solana : $2 million mcap 
3. $NEIRO on ETH: $25 million mcap
4. $NEIRO cto on ETH: $32 million mcap

The first week was an epic battle between both #SOL $NEIRO coins that we all saw happen on our timeline - one was claiming to be a community driven coin and the other being called the cabal coin. 

Simply by looking at the market caps we can see there‚Äôs 1 $NEIRO coin out of the 4 that has pretty much died. 

The number #2 coin on $SOL 

The original $SOL based $NEIRO is still alive and well at $10 million mcap with a thriving community still active. 

Now $NEIRO #3 on #ETH reached the highest mcap of them all, at the fastest rate - $300 million mcap and became the clear winner of the pack a couple weeks ago but has since gone down. 

Currently it‚Äôs retraced back down pretty heavily and is now sitting around a $30M mcap and going neck and neck with the CTO $NEIRO on #ETH which is at a $32M mcap.

Now let‚Äôs be very clear that if all 4 $NEIRO communities could agree to get behind the same $NEIRO coin - this would already be at a billion dollar mcap, but things don‚Äôt always work that way. 

I wish there was a way for us all to come together and get behind the same $NEIRO coin and hold to the bull run of 2025 and be ahead of the curve. 

At the end of the day the $NEIRO narrative is there and stronger than ever which is why so many communities are forming around this dog coin. 

The original owner of the #Dogecoin dog (who sadly recently passed away) got a new pup and named her $NEIRO who is rightfully #Dogecoin sister. 

That narrative is never going to change and it will probably be one of the biggest narratives going into the next bull run given the fact that $DOGE is still a top 10 cryptocurrency, the original meme coin and is the coin that started the bull run last crypto cycle. 

Keep that in mind. 

As things play out the way they are now, I obviously have a dog in this fight because I bought a lot of $NEIRO on #ETH and I‚Äôm down a lot right now - but I‚Äôm sure everyone wants their $NEIRO coin to be at the top and be the winner. 

I still believe the one I hold a bag of will survive this and push ahead again back to All Time Highs, but no one knows which $NEIRO will hit $1 Billion mcap and beyond first, but there‚Äôs no point in hating on all the other $NEIRO communities no matter how passionate we are about our own $NEIRO. 

At the end of the day.

May the best $NEIRO win üöÄ
